   EVALUATION OF Non-Intrusive Technologies For Traffic Detection

   Welcome to the "NIT" project website. The purpose of this website is to
   provide up-to-date results from the Minnesota DOT and FHWA's Evaluation
   of Non-Intrusive Technologies for Traffic Detection.

   The primary purpose of the NIT project is to disseminate study findings
   to traffic management and data collection practitioners around the
   country.
   http://projects.dot.state.mn.us/nit/

