   STANDARDS

   ITS STANDARDS PAGE
   This web site contains: www.its-standards.net
     * General Introductions to standards and to the U.S. DOT Standards
       Program.
     * Deployment Case studies, user guides, lessons learned, and other
       practical information for deployers
     * Slide Presentations  Slide presentations from various conferences
       and meetings.
     * Topical Reports  A variety of reports on various standards-related
       topics.

   NTCIP Case Studies:
   Three NTCIP case studies from Virginia, Washington state and
   Phoenix, AZ help ITS deployers learn from actual experiences using ITS
   standards.
   http://www.ntcip.org/library/references_n.asp

   NTCIP Guide:
   A technical guide that provides information on NTCIP standards and how
   to use them in ITS systems.
   http://www.ntcip.org/library/Guide.asp

   ITS Standards Lessons Learned Report #1:
   Insight and advice based upon the experiences of the Minnesota
   Department of Transportation's use of workshops to increase awareness
   of ITS standards.
   http://www.its-standards.net/Documents/lessons.PDF




